  "What is an augmented matrix?": "什么是扩大矩阵?",
  "The inverse of a square matrix": "平方矩阵的反方",
  "A matrix with more rows than columns": "列比列多行的矩阵",
  "A matrix filled with zeros": "充填零的矩阵表",
  "A matrix combining the coefficient matrix and the constant column of a system": "将系数矩阵和系统常列组合在一起的矩阵",
  "An augmented matrix combines the coefficient matrix and constant column into one structure, separated by a vertical bar. Row operations on this matrix solve the system.": "扩大的矩阵将系数矩阵和常列列合并成一个结构,由垂直条隔开。本矩阵上的行操作解决了系统问题。",
  "What is Gaussian elimination?": "高山的灭亡是什么?",
  "A systematic method of using row operations to convert an augmented matrix to row echelon form": "使用行操作系统化方法将增强的矩阵转换成行电子系统格式",
  "A factoring technique, particularly regarding elimination as determined by": "一种保因数技术,特别是按照",
  "A method for graphing systems when measured under controlled conditions": "在受控制条件下测量的图表绘制系统的方法",
  "A way to compute determinants in the context of this analysis": "在分析中计算决定因素的一种方法",
  "Gaussian elimination systematically applies row operations to transform an augmented matrix into row echelon form, from which variables are found by back-substitution.": "Gaussian删除系统应用行操作将扩大的矩阵转换成行梯层表,从中可找到回替换变量。",
  "What is row echelon form?": "什么是Echelon排表?",
  "The identity matrix, particularly regarding right when applying fundamental principles": "身份矩阵,特别是在适用基本原则时的权利",
  "A matrix form where each leading entry is to the right of the one above, with zeros below each pivot": "矩阵表表格,其中每个主要条目均与上述条目的权利相同,零位值低于每个支点",
  "A matrix with equal rows, particularly regarding staircase as observed in standard experiments": "具有相等行数的矩阵,特别是标准实验中观察到的楼梯",
  "A matrix with all zeros, particularly regarding echelon within the typical range of values": "带有所有零位数的矩阵,特别是典型数值范围内的梯层",
  "Row echelon form has a staircase pattern where the leading nonzero entry of each row is to the right of the one in the row above, and all entries below each leading entry are zero.": "行梯层表有一个楼梯图案,每一行的前非零条目位于上行右侧,每个前条目下的所有条目为零。",
  "What is a determinant?": "什么是决定因素?",
  "The sum of all entries based on established principles": "基于既定原则的所有条目总和",
