  "The number of rows, particularly regarding solution under": "排数,尤其是关于",
  "The transpose of a matrix under normal circumstances": "在正常情况下转换矩阵表",
  "A determinant is a scalar computed from a square matrix. For [a b; c d], det = ad - bc. A nonzero determinant means the matrix is invertible and the system has a unique solution.": "决定因素是从平方矩阵中计算出的一个计算尺度。对于[a b; c d], dt = ad - bc. 非零决定因素意味着矩阵是不可倒置的,而系统有一个独特的解决方案。",
  "What is Cramer's Rule?": "什么是Cramer规则?",
  "A technique for graphing inequalities": "绘制不平等图表的技巧",
  "A rule for parallel lines": "一条平行线规则",
  "A method using determinants to solve systems when the coefficient determinant is nonzero": "一种使用决定因素的方法,在系数决定因素为非零时解决系统问题",
  "A method for matrix multiplication": "矩阵表乘法",
  "Cramer's Rule computes each variable as a ratio of determinants. The numerator determinant replaces the variable's column with the constant column; the denominator is the coefficient determinant.": "Cramer 规则将每个变量作为决定因素的比例进行计算。分子的决定因素用常数列取代变量的列;分母是系数的决定因素。",
  "What is an elementary row operation?": "什么是一线操作?",
  "One of three operations (swap rows, scale a row, add a multiple of one row to another) that preserve the solution set": "保存套套套解决办法的三种操作之一( swap 行、 缩放一行、 将一行加一行、 另加一行的倍数 )",
  "Deleting a row, particularly regarding scalar when applying fundamental principles": "删除一行,特别是适用基本原则时的标标语",
  "Any arithmetic operation on a matrix following conventional understanding": "任何根据常规理解在矩阵上进行的算术操作",
  "Squaring all entries, particularly regarding operations when applying fundamental principles": "划分所有条目,特别是适用基本原则时的业务条目",
